page.title: 09Family Life
page.content: My name is Jane and I live with my Mum and brother Charles. My Dad works abroad. I am nine years old. On Saturday I get up at eight o'clock, dress and have breakfast. After that I watch television or go for a walk with my brother. I play with my pets for a bit, then have lunch. I have one guinea pig, two rabbits, three dogs, two tortoises and two love birds. After lunch I go to Dundee by bus for my Highland Dancing lessons. I finish dancing, which is one of my hobbies, at four o'clock. I get a bus home, and after tea I watch Television. I go to bed at eight or nine o'clock.
